</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Ragefire and A way for us to help each other</span><hr size=1> Recently I witnessed the desire for clerics to obtain there epics reach a point where I just wanted to say the hell with this game. But after much consideration I thought we have this board to voice opinions and here is an idea I thought of.<br>
<br>
  Obviously from the aspect of raiding the epic is an invaluable tool and for the most part we have all helped each other in raids from time to time. So lets get a list going of all the guilds who at this time have no Cleric epic owned by a Guild cleric to make a list and we support each others quest to get one untill we all have one epic per guild supporting this suggestion. If we all band together and do this in short order we can get epics into our guilds and make raiding that much easier on our clerics.<br>
Also along the way as we are supporting each other in obtaining these items for each other as each cleric in the list gets his epic he also makes himself available when time permits to Back up those guilds still waiting on the rez stick with raids . I estimate if we were to do this in 6 months we would have 24 guilds with at least one rez stick available and although we all would love 2 or 3 per guild even having one present in a guild will make a major difference. So please dont flame lets take this problem into our own hands and stop feeding on each other. Most guilds claim they are honorable and want to help others well here is our chance to prove it lets get together and make this work.<br>
<br>
<br>
                 Wulgare Granitefist (Clan Stormbringer)<br>
